## Questions/Decisions

**Q1: Should drag-drop work on mobile?**
- Mobile touch drag can be tricky
- Options: Disable on mobile, or add "Edit Order" button with up/down arrows
- **Recommendation:** Start with desktop only, add mobile later if needed

**Q2: Should there be a "Reset to Default Order" button?**
- Useful if user messes up their order
- Could add in Settings page under "Sidebar Settings" section
- **Recommendation:** Add in Phase 2 if time permits, otherwise defer

**Q3: Should Settings be draggable or always fixed at bottom?**
- User says "replace profile with Settings" → implies fixed position
- **Decision:** Keep Settings fixed at bottom (not in drag-drop nav)

